(530, 'Bhaskar Rayavaram', 'Bhaskar Rayavaram is a Senior Leader in Medcase. He graduated from NIT Warangal (India) and also holds an executive MBA from the University of Texas, Dallas. Bhaskar is a positive influencer who inspires everybody including youngsters with his work. He is a champion of the Telugu language and is passionate about Telugu theatre and performing arts. He is an active committee member in the \'Silicon Andhra Manabadi\' organization, an institution where more than 60,000 students across the globe have learned Telugu language. He is also an active member of Radio Surabhi in the DFW area. He started a channel on Youtube called \'B+ with Bhaskar\' during the pandemic period. The show had programs about Padyalu (Telugu poems), movies, puzzles, songs, and stories recitation. B+ program picked up several charitable causes and truly lived up to the title which translates to being positive.', 'Mr. Rayavaram, true to his message of consistency and dedication, practices what he preaches - he has been exercising everyday, for 1000+ days now, including during the pandemic, and still continues to do so.', '', 'boy', '', '', 'Slide530.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'tbd', NULL),
