(542, 'p. anitha - basket ball (tamil nadu)', 'Anitha Pauldurai is an Indian basketball player who was the captain of the India women\'s Basketball team. She is the first and only Indian female player to have participated in nine ABC events. She has led the Indian team to many wins in many championships. ', 'She is only the second female basketball player to have been awarded the Padma Shri.', '', 'girl', '', '', 'Slide542.PNG', 'proposed', 'Prashanti Singh, a shooting guard for the Indian national women\'s basketball team, is first basketball player in India conferred with National Civilian Award Padma Shri in 2019.', 'book1'),
