(574, 'Dr. Seema Rao', 'Seema Rao is an Indian army official with multiple feathers in her hat. She was a Mrs India Beauty Pageant finalist. Her father was an Indian freedom fighter - Professor Ramakant Sinari. Rao has an MBA in Crisis Management. She has earned her Para Wings by skydiving in the Indian Air Force course. She is a combat shooter, Army mountaineering institute HMI medallist, 8th degree balckbelt in Martial Arts, one of the few trainers of Jeet Kune Do, and a specialist in close quarter battle. She is popular by her nickname, Wonder Woman of India. For her incredible work, she has been awarded the Nari Shakti Puraskar. ', 'Rao and her husband have collectively taught 15,000 soldiers and have also created The Rao System of Reflex Fire, for CQB.', '', 'girl', '', '', 'Slide574.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'tbd', 'book1'),
