(578, 'CA Bhavani Devi', 'Bhavani Devi is an Indian sabre fencer. She was born in Chennai, Tamilnadu and appeared at her first international event at the age of 14. She has won many medals at various international events. Two gold medals at the Commonwealth Games, a silver and a bronze at the Asian U23 Fencing Championships, a bronze at the Asian Junior and Cadet Fencing Championship, and a bronze and two silver medals at the Junior Commonwealth Games make her a promising star.', 'She is the first ever Indian fencer to qualify for the Olympics as she was able to participate in the 2020 Summer Olympics', '', 'girl', '', '', 'Slide578.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'tbd', 'book1'),
