(601, 'Popuri Lalitha Kumari (Writer)', 'Popuri Lalita Kumari, popularly known by her pseudonym Volga, is a Telugu author. She was born in Guntur, Andhra Pradesh and completed her MA in Telugu Literature from Andhra University. Along with being a wrter, she is also a professor and the head of scripting division in Tollywood. Volga is famous for her feminist works which create awarensess of the hardships women face, predominantly in India. She has also authored, co-authored, and translated many novels and plays. She has written many famous books such as Svechcha, The Liberation of Sita, Nurella Chalam, etc.', 'Her short story compilation, \'Vimuktha Katha Samputi\' won her the prestigious Sahitya Akademi Award.', '', 'girl', '', '', 'Slide601.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'edit (why the name \'olga\')', 'book1'),
