(627, 'Prakashi Tomar  ', 'Prakashi Tomar is an Indian sharpshooter from Johri village, Uttar Pradesh. She is also regarded as one of the oldest sharpshooters in the world. She was married to Jai Singh and has a daughter, Seema Tomar. When her daughter joined the Johri Rifle Club, Prakashi went along. She shocked the coach and everyone there when she shot the taret skillfully while showing Seema how to hold the gun. The coach, Farooq Pathan advised her to join the academy and since then, she won over 25 national and international championships. Prakashi also entered a competition and won with the Deputy Inspector General of Delhi Police. She is also known as the Revolver Dadi (Revolver Grandma).', 'Saand Ki Ankh is a biopic based on Prakashi and her sister-in-law Chando Tomar where Taapsee Pannu plays the role of Prakashi.', '', 'girl', '', '', 'Slide627.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'tbd', 'book1'),
