(631, 'Sridevi', 'Sridevi was an illustrious Indian film actress who was popularly known as the \'First Female Superstar\' of Indian cinema. She was in the industry for over 50 years and acted in Malayalam, Telugu, Tamil, and Hindi cinemas. She started her career at the young age of four with the Tamil movie Kandhan Karunai. Soon after, she debuted in Hindi and Telugu also. From then onwards, she co-starred with many hit actors, including Rajnikanth, Kamal Hassan, N.T.R. Sr., Nagarjuna, Dharmendra, Rajesh Khanna, etc. She delivered many hits including Mom, English Vinglish, Nagina, and Chandni. On 24 February, 2018 she died in Dubai after drowning in the washroom.', 'She was awarded with the prestigious Padma Shri for her work in the field of cinema.', '', 'girl', '', '', 'Slide631.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'tbd', 'book1'),
