(649, 'Vanisri ', 'Vanisri was a Indian actress known for her work in Telugu, Tamil, and Kannada films. She was born in Nellore on 3rd August, 1948. She made her debut in 1962 with the Telugu movie Bhishma. She starred in many super hits including Rangula Ratnam, Sri Krishna Tulabharam, Dussehra Bullodu, etc. Vanisri has worked with many super stars including Krishna (Marapurani Katha, Ganga Manga), Akkineni Nageswara Rao (Atmiyulu, Dasara Bullodu), and Sivaji Ganesan (Nirai Kudam, Vani Rani).  ', 'Vanisri has won three Filmfare Awards South, the Nandi award and Tamil Nadu State Film Award.', '', 'girl', '', '', 'Slide649.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'tbd', 'book1'),
