(667, 'Zoya Agrawal', 'Zoya Agarwal is an Indian commerical pilot who works in Air India. She took the aviation course alongside her college and topped in both of the exams. Though she recieved a lot of criticism, she went on to be the youngest female pilot to fy a Boeing-777 in 2013. She has also saved a passenger\'s life, when she took the decision to return to Delhi midway, after she got to know that a lady on board was very unwell. In August 2022, Zoya was invited to the US-based Louis A.Turpen aviation museum,  and was recognized as having an illustrious career in the aviation field as well as inspiring millions of young girls.', 'Zoya captained an all-female crew in 2021 from San Fransisco to Bengaluru which is one of the longest non-stop air-routes in the world.', 'Pilot', 'girl', 'NA', 'Pilot', 'Slide667.PNG', 'Art Work Done', '', 'book1'),
