(670, 'Nafisa Ali', 'Nafisa Ali is an Indian actress, politician (All India Trinamool Congress), and social activist. She was born in Kolkata, West Bengal to a Bengali-Muslim father and Roman Catholic mother. She has achievements in many fields and was also a national level swimmming champion and a jockey. Ali has acted in several Bollywood films, the significant being Junoon with Shashi Kapoor, Major Saab with Amitabh Bachchan, etc. She previously worked with Indian National Congress but is currently a part of the AITC.', 'Nafisa Ali won the Femina Miss India title in 1976.', NULL, 'girl', NULL, NULL, 'Slide670.PNG', 'Art Work Done', 'tbd', 'book1'),
